title: Openstreetmap, Berlin Natural Areas, Germany, 2008
name: Openstreetmap, Berlin Natural Areas, Germany, 2008
description: This data was provided by openstreetmaps and contains detailed information on the Natural Areas in the Berlin administrative area in Germany. Natural areas include parks, forests, riverbanks, and water. data was uploaded as a poly line shape file and contains attributes for the feature type and the feature name when available.
